<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Interview Assignment — Paola Corrales</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --burgundy: #710000;
    --burgundy-light: #710000;
    --tan: #B3A188;
    --tan-light: #cfc4b2;
    --cream: #F7EDE1;
    --cream-dark: #ede0d0;
    --black: #000000;
    --gray: #6b6b6b;
    --gray-light: #e8e2d9;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .site-header {
    background: #000000;
    padding: 3rem 0 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .site-header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--tan);
  }
  .header-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .header-label {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .header-meta {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .header-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }

  /* ── Nav ── */
  .task-nav {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .nav-item {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--gray);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .nav-item:hover { color: var(--burgundy); border-bottom-color: var(--tan); }
  .nav-item.active { color: var(--burgundy); border-bottom-color: var(--burgundy); }

  /* ── Main ── */
  .main {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem 5rem;
  }

  /* ── Task Section ── */
  .task-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }
  .task-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .task-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .task-number {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--tan);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: -4px;
  }
  .task-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .task-subtitle {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
  }

  /* ── Content ── */
  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .content p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ── Step Block ── */
  .step-block {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--burgundy);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .step-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .step-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .step-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* ── Day Grid ── */
  .day-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .day-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .day-card-header {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .day-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
  }
  .day-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .day-card-body { padding: 1.25rem; }
  .day-card-body p { font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--black); }
  .day-card-body p + p { margin-top: 0.6rem; }
  .day-card-body ul { padding-left: 0; list-style: none; }
  .day-card-body ul li {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--black);
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .day-card-body ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .time-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Numbered Steps ── */
  .steps-list { counter-reset: steps; }
  .step-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .step-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .step-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .step-content strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .step-content p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: #000000; margin: 0; }

  /* ── Table ── */
  .data-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .data-table thead tr { background: var(--burgundy); color: #fff; }
  .data-table thead th { padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; font-weight: 500; }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--cream); }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(odd) { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); }
  .data-table tbody td { padding: 10px 12px; }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { color: var(--black); }
  .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(odd) td { color: var(--black); }
  .data-table tbody td:first-child { font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── Info Box ── */
  .info-box {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .info-box-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .info-box p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--black); margin: 0; }

  /* ── Survey ── */
  .survey-question {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .survey-q-header {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .survey-q-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .survey-q-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .survey-q-type {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .survey-q-body {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .survey-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .survey-option {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .survey-radio {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--tan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .survey-checkbox {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 2px solid var(--tan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .survey-textarea {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 70px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--gray);
    background: #fafafa;
    resize: vertical;
  }
  .survey-scale {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .scale-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .scale-circle {
    width: 34px; height: 34px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .scale-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gray); text-align: center; }

  /* ── Permit Cards ── */
  .permit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .permit-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .permit-card-header {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
  }
  .permit-card-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .permit-card-body { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; background: #fff; }
  .permit-meta-label {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .permit-meta-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .permit-cost {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .permit-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── Doc Rows ── */
  .doc-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .doc-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .doc-tag-col { width: 150px; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 2px; }
  .doc-req { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 4px; }
  .doc-content { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--black); }

  /* ── Phase Label ── */
  .phase-label {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .two-col-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .two-col-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── Divider ── */
  .rule { height: 1px; background: var(--tan-light); margin: 1.75rem 0; }

  /* ── Buttons ── */
  .btn-dark {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-right: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--burgundy); }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--burgundy);
    margin-right: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--burgundy); color: #fff; }

  /* ── Note Tag ── */
  .note-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    background: #fff8f0;
    border: 1px solid #e8c99a;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #8a5a00;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .note-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #e09a30; }

  /* ── Checklist ── */
  .check-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .check-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; }
  .check-item span { font-size: 14px; color: var(--black); line-height: 1.6; }
  .check-item .sub { color: var(--gray); font-size: 13px; }

  /* ── Contact Block ── */
  .contact-block {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .contact-item .label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 3px; font-weight: 500; }
  .contact-item a { color: var(--burgundy); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; }
  .contact-item p { font-size: 13px; }

  /* ── Two-col grid ── */
  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }

  /* ── Callout ── */
  .callout {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .callout-label {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .callout p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 0; }

  /* ── Itinerary timeline ── */
  .itinerary-day {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .itinerary-day-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .day-pill {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .day-title-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
  }
  .itinerary-events { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .itinerary-event {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }
  .itinerary-event:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .event-time {
    width: 70px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding-top: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .event-content { flex: 1; }
  .event-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .event-detail {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .event-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .tag-transfer { background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; }
  .tag-lodging  { background: #f7eee1; color: #8a5a00; }
  .tag-dining   { background: #f7e1e1; color: #710000; }
  .tag-activity { background: #e1f0e8; color: #1a6b3a; }
  .tag-note     { background: #e8eaf6; color: #3949ab; }

  /* ── Contacts table ── */
  .contacts-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contacts-table thead tr { background: var(--burgundy); color: #fff; }
  .contacts-table thead th { padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .contacts-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); }
  .contacts-table tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .contacts-table tbody td { padding: 10px 12px; vertical-align: top; }
  .contacts-table tbody td:first-child { font-weight: 500; color: var(--black); }
  .contact-name { font-weight: 500; color: var(--black); font-size: 13.5px; }
  .contact-org  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 2px; }
  .contact-email { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--burgundy); }
  .contact-phone { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--gray); }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  .site-footer {
    background: #000000;
    padding: 1.75rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .site-footer p { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .day-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .header-title { font-size: 30px; }
    .nav-item { padding: 0.875rem 0.75rem; font-size: 11px; }
    .header-meta { gap: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════
     HEADER
══════════════════════════════ -->
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-label">Mahler Private Staffing</div>
    <h1 class="header-title">Assessment Exercise</h1>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <span>Prepared by: Paola Corrales</span>
      <span>Submitted: Friday, May 8, 2026</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════
     NAV
══════════════════════════════ -->
<nav class="task-nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#task1" class="nav-item active">01 &nbsp;Parking Permits</a>
    <a href="#task2" class="nav-item">02 &nbsp;Mallorca Itinerary</a>
    <a href="#task3" class="nav-item">03 &nbsp;Online Survey</a>
    <a href="#task4" class="nav-item">04 &nbsp;Outlook Contacts</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════
     MAIN
══════════════════════════════ -->
<main class="main">

  <!-- ══ TASK 01 ══ -->
  <section class="task-section" id="task1">
    <div class="task-header">
      <div class="task-number">01</div>
      <div class="task-title-block">
        <h2 class="task-title">Palm Beach Parking Permits 2026</h2>
        <div class="task-subtitle">Town of Palm Beach — Permit Types, Costs &amp; Application Process</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">

      <div class="callout" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <div class="callout-label">Approach</div>
        <p>Before beginning any application, I would confirm with the principal: the property address on the island (determines eligibility: RPP vs. PPP); the number of vehicles that need permits (maximum 2 per household); whether visitor hangtags are needed and for how many guests (up to 4 per RPP household); and any commercial or staff vehicles that may require a Parking Placard Permit. This prevents wasted effort and ensures the right permit type is applied for from the start.</p>
      </div>

      <p><strong style="font-weight:500; color:var(--burgundy);">Permit Types &amp; Costs</strong></p>

      <div class="permit-grid">

        <div class="permit-card">
          <div class="permit-card-header">
            <div class="permit-card-name">Resident Parking Permit (RPP)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="permit-card-body">
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Who It's For</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text">Residents on qualifying street blocks</div>
            <div class="permit-cost">$50 / vehicle</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Key Benefit</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text" style="margin-bottom:0;">Park on your designated block; up to 48 hrs</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="permit-card">
          <div class="permit-card-header">
            <div class="permit-card-name">ParkMobile Parking Permit (PPP)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="permit-card-body">
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Who It's For</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text">All Town residents</div>
            <div class="permit-cost">$50 / vehicle</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Key Benefit</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text" style="margin-bottom:0;">2 free hours in any ParkMobile zone town-wide</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="permit-card">
          <div class="permit-card-header">
            <div class="permit-card-name">RPP Visitor Hangtag</div>
          </div>
          <div class="permit-card-body">
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Who It's For</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text">Guests of RPP-eligible residents</div>
            <div class="permit-cost">$50 / hangtag</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Key Benefit</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text" style="margin-bottom:0;">Park on resident's RPP block; up to 4 per household</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="permit-card">
          <div class="permit-card-header">
            <div class="permit-card-name">Parking Placard Permit</div>
          </div>
          <div class="permit-card-body">
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Who It's For</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text">Employers / commercial users</div>
            <div class="permit-cost">$165 / mo &nbsp;·&nbsp; $554 / 4 mo &nbsp;·&nbsp; $1,454 / yr</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-label">Key Benefit</div>
            <div class="permit-meta-text" style="margin-bottom:0;">Unlimited parking in designated commercial areas; waitlist may apply</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="step-block">
        <div class="step-label">Key Rules</div>
        <div class="step-text">Maximum of 2 permits per household for both RPP and PPP. All resident permits are valid through December 31, 2026. RPP residents may add PPP for an additional $50, or purchase PPP on its own.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="rule"></div>

      <p><strong style="font-weight:500; color:var(--burgundy);">Documents to Gather Before Applying</strong></p>

      <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <div class="doc-row">
          <div class="doc-tag-col">
            <span class="time-tag">Proof of Residency</span>
            <div class="doc-req">One required</div>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-content">Current utility bill; court-registered mortgage document, deed, condominium contract, or trust document; current Florida ID or Driver's License showing Town address; or current lease agreement (must include landlord's name and contact number). Note: hotels and short-term rentals under 12 months are not eligible.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-row">
          <div class="doc-tag-col">
            <span class="time-tag">Vehicle Information</span>
            <div class="doc-req">All required</div>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-content">Make and model; license plate number (vehicle does not need a Florida plate).</div>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-row">
          <div class="doc-tag-col">
            <span class="time-tag">Vehicle Document</span>
            <div class="doc-req">One required</div>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-content">Car registration, insurance card, or rental contract.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rule"></div>

      <p><strong style="font-weight:500; color:var(--burgundy);">How to Apply — Online</strong></p>
      <p>The Town uses the Gtechna parking permit portal, which launched for 2026 registrations on January 26, 2026.</p>

      <div class="steps-list">
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <strong>Create an account</strong>
            <p>Navigate to the <a href="https://palmbeach.gtechna.net/permit-portal/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--burgundy);">Palm Beach Permit Portal</a>, click "Sign Up" in the top right. The system automatically determines your eligibility (RPP or PPP) based on your address.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <strong>Register your vehicle</strong>
            <p>Click "Add Permit," then "Add Vehicle," enter vehicle details, and upload your Vehicle Registration and Proof of Residency.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <strong>Select your permit type</strong>
            <p>RPP residents: location defaults to your block. PPP residents: select "Townwide ParkMobile Parking Permit" from the dropdown.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <strong>Add visitor hangtags (optional — RPP residents only)</strong>
            <p>Click "Add Permit," then "Add Vehicle," toggle "Is this a visitor vehicle?" to Yes. Use format: VIS + last 5 digits of your phone number + permit number (e.g., VIS434561).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <strong>Pay and submit</strong>
            <p>Click "Add Credit Card," enter card details, accept terms, and click "Buy." Your card is not charged until the application is approved. Confirmation arrives by email.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
